The very best weeks to fly 100k with a paraglider?

Ever wondered where to go if you want to fly as many 100k's in a year as possible? XC Weeks can help you. It shows you where and in which week you'll be able to fly 100km based on the top 30'000 100km flights of the top ranked pilots in that category.

But take care, some of those places have really strong conditions in those weeks!
